name: ABC I Love You Print
description:
A fun and whimsical way to say I Love You and have it displayed on your walls. This ABC print features a cute way to say I love you, an adorable touch to any play room or nursery. Letters are in red and grey and will not be changed or customized. Print is as shown. 

NOTE: This print the actual graphic size is 8x10 and printed on an 8.5x11 piece of card stock. There will be a white border around the actual graphic. You may trim down if you like or leave as is like show in the picture.

name: Children's A Frame Tent (Gold + White)
description:
This tent is perfect for indoor movies and cupcakes, backyard campout or afternoon reading time in the shade. It stores easily under the bed or in a closet. You can take the tent apart and roll wood pieces up in fabric. Easy to assemble instructions and can be put together in just a few minutes.

The wooden tent posts are painted gold. Tent fabric is white and white chevron. Slight chevron pattern can only really be seen up close as it's white on white. 

The complete tent package measures just under 4 feet wide and long and is approximately 43 inches from the ground to the inside peak. It is perfectly sized for children under 7 and can accommodate up to three small children.

The tent fabric is attached by elastic loops at each base. This child's play tent would make a great gift for any occasion. 

We recommend not leaving your tent outdoors during bad weather. Tent fabric can be machine washed gently in cold water if necessary. Please remember that fabric colors can fade if exposed to the sun for long periods of time.

name: Zebra Print Cupcake Toppers
description:
These adorable zebra print & turquoise blue cupcake toppers are a great way to dress up cupcakes for you next party. This set includes 6 cupcake toppers.

Each cupcake topper measures 5 inches high, with the largest circle measuring 1.5 inches wide. The smaller circle is 1 inch wide. Made from heavy card stock, and attached to a white lollipop stick. 

Ready to ship, please allow 2 days for processing your order and shipping time.
